doc.previous: During the 1982 Falklands conflict termed by the Argentines Guerra de las Malvinas Guerra del Atl ntico Sur the Main Argentine Naval Fleet consisted of modernised World War II era ships one GUPPY type submarine one British built Colossus class carrier a cruiser and four destroyers supported with new ones 2 Type 42 class destroyers 3 French built corvettes and one German built Type 209 submarine This fleet was supported by several ELMA tankers and transports as well as two ice breakers polar ships
